---
import News from "./News.astro";
---

<div class="grid_3-1">
  <div>
    <h2>NEWS & EVENTS</h2>
    <p>
      The name Omada comes from the Greek word for "team" or "group", reflecting the sense of community and camaraderie that we strive to create here. Our wine tastings, cultural events, and social
      gatherings are designed to bring people together and foster connections over shared interests.
    </p>
    <p>
      Join in on one of our open wine tastings and sample the curated selection of natural wines in omada.wine’s monthly subscription box. Or come by for a plate of food and a glass of wine whenever
      one of our friends from the industry is cooking a “plat du jour”. And whenever we have a winemaker in town, Omada Wine & Deli is the place to be! Follow our events here on our website, instagram
      & facebook!
    </p>
    <a href="">Events</a>
    <News />
  </div>
  <img src="kort.webp" alt="kort" />
</div>

<style>
  .grid_3-1 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .grid_3-1 div{
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap:1rem;
    max-width: 85ch;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
  }
  p {
    font-family: "raleway", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
 h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: "aviano-sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
a {
    text-decoration: none;
    outline: 3px solid var(--bright_red);
    padding: 1rem;
    padding-inline: 2rem;
    color: var(--bright_red);
    width: 9rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: "aviano-sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid_3-1 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
